column5: Despite a case of the soggies, I was on the shore by 7:30. The bite was pretty darn good til 1:00. Lots of perch, a 12" pike, a few bass  My partner for the day got the biggest perch   Can't wait to see what the weather is like tomorrow.
Tons of Perch Bass AND fishing past Nov 15 (East of Simcoe here)  not bad at all!  nice pics, thanks for posting.  forrest
Are you still "saving up" for the fish fry?
Great report and pics bigugli  Good looking bass Thanks for sharing Leechman
Could be?   The bass went back to be caught again.
